journey
    title Doctor's Consultation Journey
    section Before the visit
      Open app: 5: Doctor
      Load or create patient note: 5: Doctor
    section During the visit
      Start recording: 5: Doctor
      Speak consultation aloud: 4: Doctor
      Live transcript appears (streamed): 4: Doctor
    section After the visit
      Tap "Clean transcript": 5: Doctor
      Tap "Generate structured summary": 5: Doctor
      Review 7-field clinical summary: 4: Doctor
      Edit note manually if needed: 3: Doctor
      Note autosaves locally (2s debounce): 5: Doctor
    section Sync
      Note syncs to backend when online (3s debounce): 4: Doctor
      Note queued if offline, replayed later: 3: Doctor
